<taxonomicName id="456351659F92CBC02569AEDCC0A9CD64" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Trechus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="333" pageNumber="334" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="apicalis" subSpecies="micans">
<emphasis id="CD45A75BF2AB13D4A204D239902C3C90" italics="true" pageId="333" pageNumber="334">Trechus apicalis micans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(LeConte), by Jeannel (1927: 172), confirmed by Lindroth (1963b: 202).
</paragraph>
